  "detailed_description": "<h1>👀</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><u>It's a game with no text.</u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The scream of consciousness dying in isolation. An interactive experience of madness.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459910/extras/dcd296a65d17f82afc3b44d6888e1497.poster.avif?t=1740984523\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459910/extras/dcd296a65d17f82afc3b44d6888e1497.webm?t=1740984523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459910/extras/dcd296a65d17f82afc3b44d6888e1497.mp4?t=1740984523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>All graphics and animation are lovingly handmade from plasticine. <br></li><li>Play time is about 20 minutes. But I hope you will remember this experience for a lifetime.<br></li><li>I swear, they forced me to make this game! Please heeeelp!<br></li><li>(distant mumbling and the sounds of struggle)<br></li><li>...<br></li><li>Two endings. The question is which of them is the worst.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<u>It's a game with no text.</u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The scream of consciousness dying in isolation. An interactive experience of madness.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459910/extras/dcd296a65d17f82afc3b44d6888e1497.poster.avif?t=1740984523\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459910/extras/dcd296a65d17f82afc3b44d6888e1497.webm?t=1740984523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459910/extras/dcd296a65d17f82afc3b44d6888e1497.mp4?t=1740984523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>All graphics and animation are lovingly handmade from plasticine. <br></li><li>Play time is about 20 minutes. But I hope you will remember this experience for a lifetime.<br></li><li>I swear, they forced me to make this game! Please heeeelp!<br></li><li>(distant mumbling and the sounds of struggle)<br></li><li>...<br></li><li>Two endings. The question is which of them is the worst.</li></ul>",
